{"tid":152674,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投]嚴選歷代十大最受香港人歡迎嘅寵物小精靈","createTime":"2017-03-12T03:35:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T14:29:46.000Z","uid":34701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb829d284810bd359af5018cedf3e4cc40aa25bf","tid":152674,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T03:35:19.000Z","msg":"比卡超一定第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終係主角，無論計知名度，周邊產品數量，遊戲動畫入面都係咁受大人細路歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外金銀版入面，果然翁同大奶罐應該都係比較受歡迎，由其網民最鍾意大奶奶嘅cap圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://yt3.ggpht.com/-UrpJTSpe01k/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAAA/Gob1DLd-oK0/s900-c-k-no-mo-rj-c0xffffff/photo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyt3.ggpht.com%2F-UrpJTSpe01k%2FAAAAAAAAAAI%2FAAAAAAAAAAA%2FGob1DLd-oK0%2Fs900-c-k-no-mo-rj-c0xffffff%2Fphoto.jpg&h=496c6afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n果然翁就因為係火戰兵團神寵深入民心，同埋佢認真起上嚟連神獸都唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n寶石版自己就鍾意巨金怪，蓋歐卡，烈空座，不過我覺得呢版冇一隻可以入到十大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n珍珠鑽石就達克萊伊同烈咬陸鯊都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑白好多都好柒，應該都係十大不入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nXYZ冇乜點睇過，不過覺得小智忍蛙都幾型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最新嘅太陽月亮隻草主好似都幾受歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://digitalspyuk.cdnds.net/16/19/768x527/gallery-1462887343-pokemon-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdigitalspyuk.cdnds.net%2F16%2F19%2F768x527%2Fgallery-1462887343-pokemon-1.png&h=1e690ee0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他就唔熟，因為我冇3DS，XY開始已經冇玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋諗到邊啲都可以提名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59fd6a48c2fe65266a2091929b452de67e19ed2a","tid":152674,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T03:37:50.000Z","msg":"啟暴龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3b6813c3e9eed9d659c12a9456823f2e171103","tid":152674,"uid":72816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T03:40:05.000Z","msg":"導電飛鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nemoemo<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ukq1oni9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fukq1oni9&h=aa2a7784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uoe7z9py\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuoe7z9py&h=460bebec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6ckqb150\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6ckqb150&h=fac0f43e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54b15de34440cbeaf972d11886e4ac7ff372ef53","tid":152674,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T03:42:13.000Z","msg":"冇玩有睇<br />\nXY我覺得仙伊貝幾正"},{"pid":"49f2fcb4b5b04d0e23987f62dcfd3d04ffcff465","tid":152674,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T03:43:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啟暴龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得姆明係因為打機勁，啲人先鍾意，但如果計動畫人氣又唔算係好高，始終唔係成日出場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果計初版十大都可能有份嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53530fc20ece1bf32986ed77ab2db39e163fcde","tid":152674,"uid":66926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T03:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8Gga65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8Gga65.jpg&h=6830e00f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8676e451597ff18c5539e14a867f479b1b292726","tid":152674,"uid":7725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T03:44:39.000Z","msg":"耿鬼for sure"},{"pid":"d27ef82643fc6af3c1cdae4ee1b0b6c684cd16c4","tid":152674,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T03:48:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>耿鬼for sure</blockquote><br />\n其實初代好難揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n耿鬼/卡比/噴火龍/姆明/伊貝呢啲都好多人鐘意，同埋第一代始終啲人都係最熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc1239cd986d3b808f8ce38ddb6802d8aeabced","tid":152674,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T03:49:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8Gga65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8Gga65.jpg&h=6830e00f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗起毒氣雙子同阿柏怪走嗰集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c2ceb806acbe8d78b3ebb24f3aa6a4cd4b9065","tid":152674,"uid":90699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T03:49:36.000Z","msg":"正電拍拍 負電拍都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d427a978aac5ba80c04d142acc06ed6d689cb0f","tid":152674,"uid":90699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T03:50:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正電拍拍 負電拍拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"721ffffd02a515b0a9ac307149c839ebe267742e","tid":152674,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>導電飛鼠<img src=\"/asse